&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule and attend internal and client meetings, taking meeting minutes and writing meeting summaries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and assign meeting actions and project deliverables, facilitating next steps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support scheduling and resourcing projects with in-house, freelance and subcontracted teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support coordination of clients and design teams between multiple time zones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Journey online production tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up, track and report on budget spend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrangle and manage media assets and relevant licensing requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the preparation of client presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
