&lt;li&gt;Experience working on cultural or exhibition-based projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in narrative-driven or culturally-led storytelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating with audio or music-focused creative teams&lt;/li&gt;
